1. *Lekara* sam posetila juče. (I visited *a doctor* yesterday.)
2. Molim te, donesi mi čašu vode za *lekaru*. (Please bring me a glass of water for *the doctor*.)
3. *Lekaru* sam objasnila svoje simptome. (I explained my symptoms to *the doctor*.)
4. Našao sam *lekare* koji se specijalizuju za tu bolest. (I found *doctors* who specialize in that disease.)
5. Juče su mi u *lekarskoj* ordinaciji izmerili krvni pritisak. (Yesterday, they measured my blood pressure at the *doctor's* office.)
6. Njena ćerka je postala *lekarka*. (Her daughter became *a doctor*.)
7. Molim vas, da li mi možete dati savet *lekara*? (Excuse me, can you give me *a doctor's* advice?)
8. *Lekari* su ga spasili nakon teške saobraćajne nesreće. (The *doctors* saved him after a severe traffic accident.)
9. *Lekare* treba poštovati jer su nam potrebni za naše zdravlje. (We should respect *doctors* because we need them for our health.)
10. *Lekar* je rekao da treba da smanjim unos soli. (The *doctor* said that I should reduce my salt intake.)